  CPU: (10) arm64 Apple M1 Max
Binaries:
  Node: 16.14.0 - /private/var/folders/jq/3x3ddtjx3rb9nwy79zxfwnj00000gn/T/xfs-ef47ac84/node
  Yarn: 3.2.4 - /private/var/folders/jq/3x3ddtjx3rb9nwy79zxfwnj00000gn/T/xfs-ef47ac84/yarn
