### Describe the bug

I expected to be able to use the `workspaces` command from inside my `package.json` scripts but installing it as a plugin or as a dev dependency did not bring it into scope.

### To reproduce

```js repro

await packageJsonAndInstall({
  scripts: {
    test: "yarn workspaces foreach exec echo hello"
